- `src/tests/unit/helpers/factories.ts` - Test infrastructure improvements

### Documentation
- `docs/LABEL-RESOLUTION-GUIDE.md` - New comprehensive guide
- `docs/BACKLOG.md` - Progress tracking and completion assessment

## Breaking Changes

